data.title: Susannah Harker
data.meta_description: All about Susannah Harker: biography, date of birth and age, place of birth, height, eye color
data.text:
Susannah Harker (Susannah Owens) - British actress. She was born April 26, 1965 in London, United Kingdom.

Best known for her work on films like Everything I Ever Wanted to Tell My Daughter About Men (2021), A Dry White Season (1989) and TV shows such as Doctor Who: Shada (2003), House of Cards (1990).
